  <num>11-742</num>
  <heading>Oaths, affirmations, and acknowledgments.</heading>
  <text>Each judge of the District of Columbia Court of Appeals and each employee of the court authorized by the chief judge may administer oaths and affirmations and take acknowledgments.</text>
